headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: The Enus Windsor Drop
content: Swing by The Diamond Casino & Resort any time this week to spin the Lucky Wheel and walk away with GTA$, RP, clothing, snacks, and mystery prizes of all sorts. This week on the podium is the Enus Windsor Drop, a luxurious drop-top convertible engineered to blow the wig right off your scalp.
